data.description: Welcome to this charming brick home with a spacious 2-car garage, boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. This well-maintained residence offers comfort and convenience in an excellent location within a welcoming and friendly neighborhood. With 1,594 square feet of living space, there's plenty of room for your family to grow and thrive. The generous lot size includes a sprinkler system and provides ample outdoor space for your enjoyment as well, the kitchen comes fully equipped with a water filtration system throughout the house, a reverse osmosis in the kitchen, refrigerator, microwave, dishwasher and stove; The two-car garage is fully insulated and has its own separate Air Conditioning. This home is an exceptional opportunity for those seeking both comfort and community. Don't miss your chance to make it your own!
